data.description: Explore the appeal of single-level living in this home within the sought-after Davidson Downs Subdivision! This meticulously crafted 3-bedroom ranch graces a half-acre corner lot with a two-car garage, complete with a drop down screen door for bug-free leisure/tinkering. The functional layout is maximized with high ceilings, quality materials, and exquisite hardwood floors throughout. The kitchen showcases stainless steel appliances, custom wood cabinetry, and granite countertops. Unwind on the screened-in porch, open deck, or sunroom. Which all have views of your private wooded retreat. Bonus features include ample attic storage and a workshop in the tall daylight entry crawlspace. Beyond its move-in readiness, the residence is in close proximity to both downtown Mooresville/Davidson, shopping, and dining, ensuring a lifestyle of utmost convenience and enjoyment.
